@David_Ornstein on Partey: &ldquo;I was told then he was desperate to join [in 2019]. Arsenal made Partey their top priority for this window. They always knew they had that &euro;50m release clause plus his desire to fall back on. They tried to negotiate a lower fee or creative solution.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
@David_Ornstein : &ldquo;Partey is a player Arsenal have admired for a great deal of time. They&rsquo;ve scouted him since 2014, actively pursued him since 2018, could&rsquo;ve got the deal done in 2019, but ended up favouring a winger - Nicolas Pepe came in.&rdquo; #afc
